Class CatalysServerLifecycleListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.server.CatalysServerLifecycleListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICatalysServerLifecycleListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EmbeddedCatalysNodeAdapterQueuedListener

    public class CatalysServerLifecycleListenerAdapter
extends Object
implements ICatalysServerLifecycleListener
    Adapter class for ICatalysServerLifecycleListener implementations only wishing to consume a subset of available events.

    This implementation just contains empty implementations of all methods.
